Nikki Cox https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nikki_Cox 0 Nicole Avery Cox (born June 2, 1978) is an American actress and comedy writer known mostly for her roles on the television series Unhappily Ever After, Las Vegas, and Nikki.
